  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the oxtail and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, lemongrass, and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chili peppers, fish sauce, palm sugar, tamarind paste, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add 1 cup of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Transfer the pot to the oven and braise the oxtail for 2 1/2 hours, or until tender.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and stir in the Thai basil and fried shallots.",
    "Serve the oxtail hot, garnished with additional Thai basil if desired."
